node.text:
Let’s get creative 🎨 We’ve resurrected #OafDrawingClub hosted by @gemmaoaf, where she creates a growing still life.

This is not about how good you are at drawing, this is the opposite of that, we are asking you to take some time out on World Mental Health awareness day. This session is built for everyone, engage your brain in something different, get messy, make mistakes, get focussed and get that dopamine pumping.

What do you need:
Access to a screen and IGTV. Paper and something to draw with, this can be anything, even a biro. It is fun to mix it up though, paint, felt tips, charcoal or baby bell wax!

This will be a mess and we can’t wait.

node.title: Oaf Drawing Club is back for #WorldMentalHealthDay
